<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="kr">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="css/join.css">
    <title>Join to MyRhy</title>
</head>
<body>
    <span id="title">최초 등록</span>
    <form action="/join" method="POST">
        <input type="text" name="displayName" placeholder="닉네임(별명)" id="nickname" class="textbox" pattern="^[a-zA-Z0-9]*$" minlength="5" maxlength="15" value="<%=name %>" required>
        <span id="name">닉네임(별명)은 5글자에서 15글자의 문자열로 이루어져야 합니다.</span>
        <input type="password" name="secondaryPassword" placeholder="2차 비밀번호" id="password" class="textbox" pattern="^[0-9]*$" minlength="4" maxlength="4" required>
        <span id="pw">2차 비밀번호는 0부터 9까지의 숫자 4자리로 이루어져야 합니다.</span>
        <input type="submit" class="button" value="완료">
    </form>
    <script src="https://code.jquery.com/jquery-3.4.1.min.js"></script>
    <script src="js/join.js"></script>
</body>
</html>